{"tid":632922,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"年年見到有On9問人去唔去Jupas interview好就好撚火滾","createTime":"2018-04-18T00:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T14:32:17.000Z","uid":34884,"like":213,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"efd5a125b6ae8cef2395503dfc000050a73a6569","tid":632922,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:24:06.000Z","msg":"認真一科interview最多咪嘥你個零鐘時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打個飛機都冇左喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話去到in得唔好扣分就話啫<br />\n人地Prof講到明只會加分唔會扣分，只係想見下班應屆DSE雞傾下計<br />\n你揀得呢科做bandA/B唔多唔少都有少少想讀呢科啦<br />\n人地Prof通常in完都會同你傾下計，又或者樓下擺booth，畀你地了解呢科多啲<br />\n<br />\n仲有人生除左見工都冇乜機會畀你試單對單in或者Panel interview，仲要完全冇成本<br />\n咪當見識下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全諗唔到有咩理由唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就當你講撚到個零鐘時間好緊要，咁你咪撚去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你又問全世界唔去會唔會扣分甚至唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你咩又要馬兒好又要馬兒唔吃草<br />\n唔in出個Conditional offer畀你好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n考得DSE都18歲大個仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己衡量下值唔值得去囉<br />\n我答你你夠高分絕大部分學科唔in都照入<br />\n但我同你講一個冇成本既interview都扭扭擰擰，就算幾撚高分，出嚟社會都係一條On9"},{"pid":"63433dca736d382583bc28fa884f8b7dff31631d","tid":632922,"uid":34884,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:26:09.000Z","msg":"除左撞正有緊要事（不過通常有得改時間）<br />\n邊個仲開Post問人去唔去interview好<br />\n<br />\n我祝你Jupas no offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85e32c51d59c6ec52303bf6a714f14ffa8b2cbc","tid":632922,"uid":53278,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"除非你好outstanding<br />\n唔係既根本冇人會記得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904e749ecf8317bc5fc11933f9f418078cd5f670","tid":632922,"uid":26167,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"當年ust bba係放榜前搞interview<br />\n我同我啲frd擺band a得我有啲in<br />\n去到係宣傳佢果科多過in我地<br />\n問番同組啲人，個個名校擺ust bba band b band c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過當年同我地傾計果個師姐樣靚長腿短褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：cu ibba grad"},{"pid":"beb4dc9e7123a4a1e209a5cd43120f0333a26237","tid":632922,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c85e32c51d59c6ec52303bf6a714f14ffa8b2cbc","tid":632922,"uid":53278,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"除非你好outstanding<br />\n唔係既根本冇人會記得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:13:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得自己都冇所謂啦<br />\n<br />\n根本去interview係百利而無一害<br />\n當見識下都好啦"},{"pid":"2785fa000fdc8eee6d2a3e89b7f3dc3bf5b5512f","tid":632922,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"904e749ecf8317bc5fc11933f9f418078cd5f670","tid":632922,"uid":26167,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"當年ust bba係放榜前搞interview<br />\n我同我啲frd擺band a得我有啲in<br />\n去到係宣傳佢果科多過in我地<br />\n問番同組啲人，個個名校擺ust bba band b band c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過當年同我地傾計果個師姐樣靚長腿短褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：cu ibba grad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"姐姐我想入你個系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d586fbe