d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常『唔識諗』既人，人地叫佢應該諗都唔使諗去in<br />\n<br />\n係都要唔去，我真係唔太明佢地諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ea98637f67ff2ed41a42e2b1737019bbc43535","tid":632922,"uid":34884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cc6d6be456dedeb7ad2772ca21945267931370f9","tid":632922,"uid":134438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"個時以為自己炒左中文跟著冇去到都照入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早知去嚟玩下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"我調返轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年我以為自己炒左英文<br />\n但都照去interview<br />\n<br />\n最後收到電話同Email叫我放A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8284d828a22249df26920cf504716b499d2b57","tid":632922,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e1028ee6e4f129ef2b5e857ad7dc1c96a34aac","tid":632922,"uid":22808,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:58:21.000Z","msg":"真心，各位中六嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n如果你jupas 擺嘅choice 都唔洗in <br />\n其實呢科讀唔讀都罷，因為啲老師都冇重視過啲ug<br />\n<br />\n呢啲科一定好撚垃圾，到時個個同學都放負屌冇工開<br />\n<br />\n然後你會讀到好灰，灰撚到懷疑人生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大學第一學位係你中學六年黎，努力嘅證明。<br />\n唔好是是旦旦亂揀科，一定要睇過悶曬嘅課程內容先好揀，唔係你定後悔。"},{"pid":"85e6af2620388c032aee48b28b0d1786c8139d50","tid":632922,"uid":182423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"去下又無死既"},{"pid":"2dd38ed3d907f1fd6d75214121e2b0c60d363d4c","tid":632922,"uid":16869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"講得好"},{"pid":"b72535bd6527e66e69b7a39fec23de40608e98a0","tid":632922,"ui